Sir, Kuzumi works
at a lift maintenance company,

00:06:54.430 --> 00:06:57.630
he was responsible for the
maintenance of the lift there.

00:06:57.710 --> 00:07:00.790
He could tamper with it
if he wanted to?

00:07:00.870 --> 00:07:03.590
The security camera was broken,
so we don't know the details.

00:07:03.670 --> 00:07:07.310
However, Kuzumi's toolbox
was left at the crime scene.

00:07:08.590 --> 00:07:11.160
By the way,
Kuzumi's subordinate said

00:07:11.240 --> 00:07:13.560
that he was pretty obsessed
with lifts.

00:07:13.640 --> 00:07:15.520
Obsessed with lifts!

