And Nana is still in custody today?

00:08:21.520 --> 00:08:25.000
Someone murdered another person
and put Nana through this.

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:31.800
You borrowed someone's smartphone,
wrote you want a murder-swap,

00:08:31.880 --> 00:08:35.760
and put Mr. Hosokawa's photo
on the forum.

00:08:35.840 --> 00:08:37.080
I told you, l--

00:08:37.160 --> 00:08:39.080
A week after the first message
was written,

00:08:39.160 --> 00:08:42.000
Mr. Hosokawa himself
called the police,

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:45.560
and without a doubt,
you are the murderer.

00:08:45.640 --> 00:08:46.800
However, that evening,

00:08:46.880 --> 00:08:51.920
Mr. Hosokawa was involved in a fall
with your friend, Yuzuru Kuzumi,

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:54.920
and died there.

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:57.360
I did not write that message.

00:08:57.440 --> 00:09:00.480
Did Yuzuru Kuzumi read this message?

00:09:00.560 --> 00:09:02.160
I don't know.

00:09:02.240 --> 00:09:03.600
I already told you yesterday.

00:09:03.680 --> 00:09:05.560
You've been separated for years

00:09:05.640 --> 00:09:07.960
but he didn't agree
to get a divorce,

00:09:08.040 --> 00:09:09.320
so you wanted to murder him...

00:09:09.400 --> 00:09:11.800
l've answered this question
many times as well!

00:09:11.880 --> 00:09:16.270
We were taught to ask
the same questions again and again.

00:09:16.350 --> 00:09:18.430
Why is that?

00:09:18.510 --> 00:09:20.160
Tell her why.

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:22.840
Because if you are lying,

00:09:22.920 --> 00:09:26.240
