if we ask over and over again.

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:27.560
Is that the reason?

00:09:27.640 --> 00:09:32.150
And? Have you found any hole
in what l've told you?

00:09:33.150 --> 00:09:34.070
We haven't.

00:09:34.150 --> 00:09:35.830
- Then...
- Come on!

00:09:35.910 --> 00:09:39.190
Do you know how many people
who lived in your condo died?

00:09:39.270 --> 00:09:41.230
Let us investigate it thoroughly.

00:09:41.310 --> 00:09:43.910
But it's the game...

00:09:45.630 --> 00:09:47.590
That's how tricky the case is,

00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:50.070
make sure you don't tell
another detective.

00:09:53.470 --> 00:09:57.590
I'm here because l want to help.

00:09:57.670 --> 00:09:59.310
I did nothing suspicious...

00:09:59.390 --> 00:10:00.710
Sir!

00:10:02.030 --> 00:10:03.790
You scared me!
l died for two seconds!

00:10:03.870 --> 00:10:06.190
- Sorry, sir, but...
- What is it?

00:10:06.270 --> 00:10:09.730
Is there any connection
between Mr. Kuzumi's accident

00:10:09.810 --> 00:10:11.750
and Mr. Ukita's death?

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:17.130
By the way, who among these
three people wrote Mr. Ukita's name?

00:10:17.210 --> 00:10:18.330
Three people?

00:10:18.410 --> 00:10:19.530
Well...

00:10:20.690 --> 00:10:23.050
lf Mr. Ukita was killed...

00:10:24.410 --> 00:10:28.730
that means among Mr. Tamiya,
Miss Ono and the caretaker,

00:10:28.810 --> 00:10:31.330
one of them
wrote Mr. Ukita's name, right?

00:10:31.410 --> 00:10:33.580
Yes, you're right.

00:10:33.660 --> 00:10:35.140
Who do you think it is?

00:10:35.220 --> 00:10:36.700
"301, Ono"

00:10:36.780 --> 00:10:38.140
"Caretaker, Tokoshima"

00:10:39.260 --> 00:10:40.500
Mr. Tokoshima?

00:10:40.580 --> 00:10:42.340
Why?

00:10:42.420 --> 00:10:44.540
Among the three,

00:10:44.620 --> 00:10:48.660
Mr. Tokoshima wasn't really
on good terms with Mr. Ukita.

00:10:48.740 --> 00:10:51.340
- I see.
- No matter who wrote it,

00:10:51.420 --> 00:10:54.580
the people who could've drawn
Mr. Ukita's piece of paper were...

00:10:55.820 --> 00:11:00.710
Mr. Tamiya, Xinyi, Miss Ono,

00:11:00.790 --> 00:11:04.010
Mrs. Akaike and the caretaker.

00:11:04.090 --> 00:11:05.590
There are five people.

00:11:06.950 --> 00:11:10.550
But Mrs. Akaike and the caretaker
are dead,

00:11:10.630 --> 00:11:13.760
so the people who could've killed
Mr. Ukita are...

00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:15.760
Mr. Tamiya...

00:11:17.760 --> 00:11:18.960
Xinyi...

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:22.130
and Miss Ono.

00:11:44.890 --> 00:11:45.850
l...

00:11:45.930 --> 00:11:47.090
Miss Ono.

