but this is a massage oil
made with natural ingredients.

00:12:07.610 --> 00:12:10.700
It's good for your skin
and it makes you calm too.

00:12:10.780 --> 00:12:13.820
Oh, but you see...

00:12:13.900 --> 00:12:15.180
l won't give you this.

00:12:16.180 --> 00:12:17.540
If l give it to you,

00:12:17.620 --> 00:12:20.580
