He looked exactly like the man...

00:13:51.430 --> 00:13:53.750
You see,
the man who just passed away...

00:13:53.830 --> 00:13:55.890
Oh, Yoshihiko Hakamada!

00:13:55.970 --> 00:13:58.010
- What?
