00:13:58.090 --> 00:13:59.890
also matched Kuzumi's clothes.

00:13:59.970 --> 00:14:01.690
So Kuzumi borrowed a phone

00:14:01.770 --> 00:14:05.610
and wrote the request to kill
Mr. Hosokawa on the forum?

00:14:05.690 --> 00:14:06.930
