but in other people's eyes,

00:16:57.900 --> 00:16:59.700
he was evil.

00:17:01.380 --> 00:17:02.900
That's true.

00:17:02.980 --> 00:17:04.820
What is this?

00:17:04.900 --> 00:17:06.620
Mr. Ukita loved it.

00:17:06.700 --> 00:17:09.580
I know, but bring him a fresh one.

00:17:09.660 --> 00:17:10.860
Idiot!

00:17:10.940 --> 00:17:12.700
Mr. Ukita loved one that's soft

00:17:12.780 --> 00:17:14.980
after being put in the fridge
overnight.

00:17:20.500 --> 00:17:21.980
Who killed him?

00:17:33.540 --> 00:17:35.970
"Penguin Moving Company"

00:17:43.420 --> 00:17:47.260
This is none of your business,
Mrs. lshizaki.

00:17:47.340 --> 00:17:49.020
It is my business.

